Game of Life

Goofy formatting hacks included for Linux terminals; bad times will be
had on other environments.

Build with make; requires a C++11 standard compiler.

Execution options:
	board
		No arguments, auto size board and 1 second delay between
		generations.

	board <delay>
		One argument, auto size board and $delay milliseconds between
		generations.

	board <delay> <width> <height>
		Three arguments, $width by $height board and $delay milliseconds
		between generations.
